com.viaoa.web

Interface OAJspComponent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    OABackgroundImage, OABadge, OAButton, OAButtonList, OACheckBox, OACombo, OAComboBox, OADialog, OAExpander, OAFileInput, OAGrid, OAHtmlElement, OAHtmlSelect, OAImage, OALabel, OALink, OAList, OAListing, OAPassword, OAPopover, OAPopup, OAPopupList, OARadio, OAServletBackgroundImage, OAServletImage, OASlimscroll, OAStyledTextArea, OATabbedPane, OATable, OATextArea, OATextField, OATree, OATreeTableController

    public interface OAJspComponent
extends Serializable
    Interface used for implementing JSP controls, to be contained by OAForm. OAForm handles the html form and interacts with the components.
    Author:
    vvia
